{"tid":2307876,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"點解有線新聞編採記者可以即時決定辭職抗議，泛民議員要典嚟典去數個月先辭？","createTime":"2020-12-01T12:45:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T14:54:30.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"04bc9a6ae6ddb2996843cfbf88f934e7624992d4","tid":2307876,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T12:45:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1563041-20201201.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1563041-20201201.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=3wrM%2FJom4zLweqSprMIx0urBpkLuHOqafswNxXmn3gI%3D&h=3cbc8a80\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1563041-20201201.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=787ff7b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1563041-20201201.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">有線新聞5名採主及11名記者辭職   對高層做法感憤怒</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n有線新聞港聞組5名採主及11名記者即時辭職，抗議有線新聞解僱約40名新聞部員工，對高層一手摧毀有線新聞部表示極度遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n16人發表共同聲明指，被被解僱的大部分是資深員工，服務新聞部多年，部分在各部門過往表現突出，名單更包括專題組新聞刺針全組記者。<br />\n<br />\n他們曾向4名高層包括謝燕娜、許方輝、李臻、陳興昌要求交代裁員準則，但得到的回應只是架構重組及節省資源，更有人以「爛仔」形容同事，裁員前亦沒有知會或諮詢各部門主管，完全無視員工的付出，做法極不尊重，令人憤怒。<br />\n<br />\n辭職的包括總採主林穎茵、兩名助理總採主曾楚群及林妙茵、採主雷子樂、助理採主陳婉婷，以及另外11名港聞記者。"},{"pid":"b5d3ca34034fa729eb2ac4adbfd970af500762a1","tid":2307876,"uid":172443,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T12:55:28.000Z","msg":"十萬人工同二萬人工點比<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9dde71148f0e6c4867b1cc078d9a055e71bf3b1","tid":2307876,"uid":261873,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b5d3ca34034fa729eb2ac4adbfd970af500762a1","tid":2307876,"uid":172443,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T12:55:28.000Z","msg":"十萬人工同二萬人工點比<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\